All Implemented Interfaces:
ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler
public class TEIAffiliationAddressSaxParser
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler

SAX parser for affiliation+address sequences encoded in the TEI format data. Segmentation of tokens must be identical as the one from pdf2xml files to that training and online input tokens are identical.

Author:
Patrice Lopez
